# to switch to use AJAX to replace form for handling data 

- in controller.php : un-comment "// FOR USING AJAX " part 
- in views/viewall.php  remove "style : display : none; " of 4 elements right bellow  <!--FOR USING AJAX--> lines 
and set display: none for <!--FOR USING PURE PHP--> 
- in views/update : set display:none  / comment all lines , elements right bellow  <!--FOR USING PURE PHP--> 
and display the ones bellow <!--FOR USING AJAX-->